description: This token indicates the city's recognition of services performed. It can be redeemed at a merchant for a small cash value, or may be saved for spending during city festival days.
A blackened, metal coin, stamped with an icon of flame, in honor of Fennin Ro and Solusek Ro. Scorched Sky Celebration merchants will accept this as currency!
A token for honored players who inhabit Norrath. Speak to Tark Validus or Toowik Mclure in Freeport or Qeynos.
A specially minted coin in honor of Norrath's victory over Kerafyrm. Very few merchants will accept this as currency!
Resumes for Agents who just didn't make the cut. Perhaps these can be traded for something else of value. This item is not considered a currency and will not double for members or server bonuses.
A specially minted coin in honor of Heroes' Festival. Very few merchants will accept this as currency!
This currency is used to purchase items from the Goblin Games.
This currency is used by dungeon builders and dungeon adventurers alike!
A newly minted coin in honor of Erollisi Day. Very few merchants will accept this as currency!
A wooden coin circulated in honor of Brewday. Very few merchants will accept this as currency!
